  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And he said unto them, ye are the chief of the fathers of the Levites,.... Of the families of the Levites, heads of their fathers' houses: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "sanctify yourselves, both ye and your brethren; respectively under each, whose numbers are before given, by washing their bodies and clothes, and abstaining from their wives: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "that you may bring up the ark of the Lord God of Israel unto the place that I have prepared for it; 2 Samuel 6:17. ",
